headline.main: HITLER, AT FRONT, TALKS WITH CIANO; Parley With Italian Foreign Minister Held to Center on Military Situation

lead_paragraph: BERLIN, Oct. 25 (AP) -- Reichfuehrer Hitler conferred with Count Ciano, Italian Foreign Minister, for two hours today at the German front headquarters in a meeting officially described as occurring "in the spirit of their two countries' proven comradeship in arms."
